pointed out in the last

00:13:42.020 --> 00:13:43.960
episode in the Hangout.

00:13:43.960 --> 00:13:47.150
Things like Settings or Help
or About, or even just more

00:13:47.150 --> 00:13:51.140
stuff, they generally don't
belong immediately on screen

00:13:51.140 --> 00:13:56.660
