navigation area.

00:13:56.660 --> 00:13:59.350
And we've specifically outlined
that things like

00:13:59.350 --> 00:14:02.310
Settings, Help, About, Terms
of Service, Privacy Policy,

00:14:02.310 --> 00:14:04.680
those should really belong in
the action bar overflow.

00:14:04.680 --> 00:14:07.030
So when you press this action
bar overflow here in the

00:14:07.030 --> 00:14:09.020
action bar, you should see
things like Settings

00:14:09.020 --> 00:14:10.770
