bar spinner.

00:14:30.550 --> 00:14:34.860
In this case, we're already
using tabs to switch between

00:14:34.860 --> 00:14:36.300
yesterday, today,
and tomorrow.

00:14:36.300 --> 00:14:38.990
And so we decided to switch to
the action bar spinner as the

00:14:38.990 --> 00:14:44.070
top level core structural
navigational component.

00:14:44.070 --> 00:14:46.300
And so there you can switch
between matches,

00:14:46.300 --> 00:14:49.195
competitions, and teams.

00:14:49.195 --> 00:14:52.640
And it makes clear the three
main sections of the app.

